  "description": "JP Adopt-a-People-Group pilot (demo-jp): a relying-app prototype for FPG adoption brokerage. Public capability UX + adopter/facilitator onboarding that connects to Impact (demo-sso), which holds the person/org data + signed MOU/WEA and delegates scoped access (spec 236). Demo only — 'JP' is a placeholder; no real-program affiliation.",
